1
00:00:49,679 --> 00:00:50,679
I called you so many times.

2
00:00:50,759 --> 00:00:51,640
Why didn't you answer?

3
00:00:51,840 --> 00:00:52,560
I was busy with work.

4
00:00:54,119 --> 00:00:54,880
No time to answer.

5
00:00:56,479 --> 00:00:57,759
No time to contact me,

6
00:00:58,479 --> 00:00:59,759
but you had time for other female doctors,

7
00:00:59,880 --> 00:01:01,240
listening to the sea, feeling the breeze.

8
00:01:01,960 --> 00:01:03,439
You really know how to enjoy life.

9
00:01:04,439 --> 00:01:05,079
You followed me?

10
00:01:05,239 --> 00:01:06,680
I wanted to see your life now.

11
00:01:07,319 --> 00:01:08,439
The Danio I used to know

12
00:01:08,719 --> 00:01:10,159
was the center of everyone's attention.

13
00:01:10,519 --> 00:01:12,680
Why settle for a place like this now?

14
00:01:14,519 --> 00:01:15,599
And after being together all these years,

15
00:01:15,840 --> 00:01:17,040
Dr. Jiang never reached out to her?

16
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:17,640
Right.

17
00:01:17,719 --> 00:01:19,560
Qiyue, that periodontitis patient earlier,

18
00:01:19,640 --> 00:01:20,719
remember to follow up tomorrow.

19
00:01:20,719 --> 00:01:21,640
Check on the recovery.

20
00:01:21,760 --> 00:01:22,400
Got it.

21
00:01:24,719 --> 00:01:25,400
Dr. Tang,

22
00:01:26,239 --> 00:01:28,280
that pretty woman who came earlier,

23
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:30,359
she's Dr. Jiang's girlfriend, right?

24
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:32,760
She doesn't seem like your average woman.

25
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:34,920
That bag of hers, it's a limited edition.

26
00:01:35,879 --> 00:01:37,120
You think a stunning beauty like that

27
00:01:37,239 --> 00:01:38,920
could fall for a weirdo like Dr. Jiang?

28
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:40,560
Her taste is quite unique.

29
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:42,680
Right, I just can't figure it out.

30
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:44,719
Is she his ex or his current girlfriend?

31
00:01:44,799 --> 00:01:45,439
Probably his current girlfriend.

32
00:01:45,519 --> 00:01:46,560
Okay, enough gossiping.

33
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:51,480
Lin Fei'er,

34
00:01:51,959 --> 00:01:53,040
know your place.

35
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:54,840
We've already decided to Part ways.

36
00:01:55,159 --> 00:01:57,040
What right do you have to judge my life?

37
00:01:57,359 --> 00:01:59,159
I never said I wanted to break up with you.

38
00:02:01,079 --> 00:02:02,680
Then who's been running away all these years?

39
00:02:03,719 --> 00:02:05,040
Not answering calls, not replying to WeChat.

40
00:02:05,319 --> 00:02:06,920
Yet international summits and academic forums,

41
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:08,520
you never missed a single one.

42
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:10,560
How can you even say that?

43
00:02:12,599 --> 00:02:13,159
Yes,

44
00:02:13,879 --> 00:02:15,080
when you needed me the most,

45
00:02:15,199 --> 00:02:16,240
I wasn't there for you.

46
00:02:16,919 --> 00:02:17,560
But that doesn't mean

47
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:19,039
I forgot what we had.

48
00:02:24,319 --> 00:02:24,960
Danio,

49
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:27,439
do you remember this ring?

50
00:02:28,759 --> 00:02:30,199
Back when we were together,

51
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,199
you engraved it yourself.

52
00:02:32,599 --> 00:02:33,680
Didn't we promise

53
00:02:33,759 --> 00:02:35,639
to wear it together as we rose to the top?

54
00:02:36,439 --> 00:02:37,240
All these years,

55
00:02:37,439 --> 00:02:38,000
no matter where I went,

56
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:39,319
I never forgot.

57
00:02:39,879 --> 00:02:41,680
I just wanted to keep that promise.

58
00:02:43,479 --> 00:02:44,439
You must have forgotten.

59
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,719
The one who wanted to reach the top

60
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,599
was always just you.

61
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:50,719
Danio,

62
00:02:51,879 --> 00:02:52,439
yes,

63
00:02:53,159 --> 00:02:54,560
I was too young back then,

64
00:02:55,039 --> 00:02:56,159
too eager for success.

65
00:02:56,479 --> 00:02:57,840
A lot of my decisions were impulsive.

66
00:02:58,080 --> 00:02:58,639
But all these years,

67
00:02:58,719 --> 00:03:00,520
I've never forgotten what we had.

68
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:02,240
I came back now for you.

69
00:03:03,479 --> 00:03:04,719
I really want to make up for

70
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:06,080
all the years we missed.

71
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,000
No one

72
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:15,840
can stand still for ten years

73
00:03:16,439 --> 00:03:17,759
waiting for someone to come back.

74
00:03:20,599 --> 00:03:21,960
If you'd truly moved on,

75
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,960
you wouldn't still be alone after all these years.

76
00:03:24,599 --> 00:03:26,039
Don't flatter yourself.

77
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,120
I'm just waiting for someone

78
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:30,479
worth moving forward for.

79
00:03:45,159 --> 00:03:46,199
Thank you, thank you.

80
00:03:46,919 --> 00:03:47,560
You're welcome.

81
00:03:47,599 --> 00:03:48,639
Take care of yourself and the baby.

82
00:03:48,639 --> 00:03:49,280
Dr. Tang,

83
00:03:49,599 --> 00:03:50,879
are you still single?

84
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:52,919
How about we add each other on WeChat?

85
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:54,319
I'd love to introduce my brother to you.

86
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:56,479
He's tall, quiet, and has a great job.

87
00:03:56,599 --> 00:03:58,479
Most importantly, he treats his wife well.

88
00:03:58,599 --> 00:03:59,560
If you marry him,

89
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:01,439
he'll never let you down, not even a bit.

90
00:04:01,639 --> 00:04:03,520
I'll have them send you his contact info later.

91
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,280
If you have any dental issues in the future,

92
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,319
feel free to come ask me.

93
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,719
But as for the matchmaking,

94
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:09,240
let's set that aside for now.

95
00:04:09,879 --> 00:04:11,719
Our Dr. Tang already has a suitor.

96
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,400
When she stands next to Dr. Chen,

97
00:04:13,479 --> 00:04:14,439
they're quite the sight to behold.

98
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:16,680
What a shame.

99
00:04:16,839 --> 00:04:18,519
I finally found such a lovely young lady,

100
00:04:18,639 --> 00:04:20,920
beautiful and skilled in every way.

101
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:23,800
Whoever marries you will be one lucky man.

102
00:04:24,279 --> 00:04:25,480
Come on, I'll walk you downstairs.

103
00:04:25,879 --> 00:04:26,560
Go ahead.

104
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:27,839
Are you single?

105
00:04:28,079 --> 00:04:28,920
I...

106
00:04:38,279 --> 00:04:39,480
I just came to tell you,

107
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,560
Lin Fei'er and I, well...

108
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:42,519
Your ex-girlfriend, right?

109
00:04:43,519 --> 00:04:44,959
She came specifically to ask to get back together.

110
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:46,040
What a great opportunity.

111
00:04:46,399 --> 00:04:48,120
Dr. Jiang, you should cherish it.

112
00:05:24,879 --> 00:05:26,040
I'll make you believe

113
00:05:26,439 --> 00:05:27,279
that other than me,

114
00:05:28,079 --> 00:05:29,120
no one's more right for you.

115
00:05:33,519 --> 00:05:34,399
Let me tell you,

116
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:36,160
I pulled a few strings last night

117
00:05:36,319 --> 00:05:37,639
and looked into The Awesome Ex.

118
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:38,639
Guess what?

119
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:39,920
I had no idea until I checked.

120
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,079
When this woman goes hard,

121
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:42,319
no man can keep up.

122
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:44,079
Over a dozen major papers abroad,

123
00:05:44,199 --> 00:05:45,240
all written by her.

124
00:05:45,959 --> 00:05:46,920
Now that she's back in China,

125
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,519
top hospitals in Pingjin are fighting over her.

126
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:50,160
She's seriously living the dream.

127
00:05:53,879 --> 00:05:54,480
But still,

128
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:56,759
a sharp-tongued, fussy guy like Jiang Tiancai

129
00:05:57,160 --> 00:05:59,160
just doesn't deserve The Awesome Ex.

130
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:01,519
Isn't it great being a fabulous single woman?

131
00:06:01,839 --> 00:06:03,800
Why be Hung up on a lost cause?

132
00:06:04,079 --> 00:06:04,680
I just don't get it.

133
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:07,040
Hey, what's so bad about Dr. Jiang?

134
00:06:10,399 --> 00:06:12,480
Don't tell me you're blinded by his looks.

135
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,839
Aren't you into Dr. Chen?

136
00:06:15,759 --> 00:06:16,319
Qiao Qiyue,

137
00:06:16,439 --> 00:06:18,040
where'd you get the idea I like Dr. Chen?

138
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:19,439
That's just respect for a senior colleague.

139
00:06:19,519 --> 00:06:20,279
Respect, okay?

140
00:06:21,639 --> 00:06:22,720
You didn't deny it though.

141
00:06:23,439 --> 00:06:25,439
Don't tell me you've really got a thing for Jiang Tiancai.

142
00:06:31,759 --> 00:06:32,680
Even if I did,

143
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:34,399
what good is one-sided love?

144
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:38,040
Then he's the one with no taste.

145
00:06:39,319 --> 00:06:41,000
But Dr. Chen's feelings for you

146
00:06:41,079 --> 00:06:42,079
are written all over his face.

147
00:06:42,519 --> 00:06:43,399
You can't tell?

148
00:06:44,879 --> 00:06:45,720
Does he really?

149
00:06:47,639 --> 00:06:48,360
Forget it.

150
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,279
You can't see what's right in front of you.

151
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,079
Anyway, just remember,

152
00:06:52,519 --> 00:06:54,000
not a single man is any good.

153
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,800
Only your girl here

154
00:06:56,439 --> 00:06:58,319
will stand on your side, united.

155
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:03,959
Okay, hurry out and check

156
00:07:04,079 --> 00:07:05,079
when my patient's arriving.

157
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:06,199
I'm leaving.

158
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:08,079
Go, go, go.

159
00:07:08,279 --> 00:07:09,639
Don't keep my patient waiting. I'm off.

160
00:07:09,759 --> 00:07:10,920
Go, go, go.

161
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,279
Morning, Dr. Jiang. Morning, Dr. Jiang.

162
00:07:28,879 --> 00:07:30,279
Are you planning to spend the rest of your life

163
00:07:30,639 --> 00:07:32,839
just fixing teeth and filling cavities?

164
00:07:41,839 --> 00:07:43,279
That parotid tumor patient I consulted

165
00:07:43,399 --> 00:07:44,360
online for free last night,

166
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,560
which exam room was he assigned to?

167
00:07:46,079 --> 00:07:47,759
He just switched to Dr. Chen's appointment.

168
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:48,800
Another one who changed his mind.

169
00:07:49,279 --> 00:07:50,439
Dr. Jiang, you know

170
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:52,120
our department mostly handles dental work.

171
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,160
So when patients come in

172
00:07:53,279 --> 00:07:54,439
and see Dr. Chen downstairs,

173
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:55,680
they naturally change their minds.

174
00:07:56,519 --> 00:07:58,600
How about this, I've got a few whitening cases here.

175
00:07:58,800 --> 00:07:59,759
Could you take care of them?

176
00:08:09,279 --> 00:08:10,759
He actually didn't get angry. Right.

177
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:20,519
Dr. Jiang, thank you so much.

178
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:23,600
After the way my old man treated you last time,

179
00:08:24,399 --> 00:08:26,399
you didn't hold it against us

180
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:29,040
and still agreed to treat his teeth.

181
00:08:29,759 --> 00:08:30,439
It was all a misunderstanding.

182
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,439
Don't take it to heart.

183
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:34,679
Come on.

184
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:35,919
Take it slow.

185
00:08:45,159 --> 00:08:47,120
When my son left home,

186
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,759
he wasn't much older than you.

187
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:54,759
Ten years now.

188
00:08:57,519 --> 00:08:59,960
That ungrateful boy,

189
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,879
he hasn't called home

190
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:04,360
even once.

191
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:07,600
Why are you crying again all of a sudden?

192
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:09,399
Don't cry.

193
00:09:10,759 --> 00:09:12,080
Our son got married.

194
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:13,360
He didn't abandon you.

195
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:16,000
Talk some sense into your mom.

196
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,799
Don't act up on such a happy day.

197
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:20,000
Sobbing like that.

198
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:22,960
Sorry about this, Dr. Jiang.

199
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:25,799
Old man, you're getting confused again.

200
00:09:26,039 --> 00:09:27,600
This is Dr. Jiang.

201
00:09:28,799 --> 00:09:29,799
What doctor?

202
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:35,799
You took your wife to the doctor?

203
00:09:36,919 --> 00:09:37,759
What did the doctor say?

204
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:38,919
Is it a boy or a girl?

205
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:43,559
A boy.

206
00:09:44,679 --> 00:09:46,200
Boy or girl, it's all the same.

207
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:49,000
As long as it's healthy and safe,

208
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,559
that's all that matters.

209
00:09:50,919 --> 00:09:51,919
Your mom and I,

210
00:09:52,639 --> 00:09:53,879
we don't have much to offer.

211
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:56,600
We can't help you much down the road.

212
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:59,679
But leave the babysitting to us.

213
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:02,120
You two go do what you need to do.

214
00:10:10,039 --> 00:10:11,480
Uncle Ge, crowning your natural teeth

215
00:10:11,559 --> 00:10:13,200
isn't very feasible.

216
00:10:14,039 --> 00:10:16,039
So the most suitable option for now

217
00:10:16,399 --> 00:10:17,480
is wearing a removable denture.

218
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:20,919
You'll need to keep a close eye on

219
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:22,200
Uncle Ge's oral condition,

220
00:10:22,519 --> 00:10:23,840
to keep him from swallowing or inhaling it.

221
00:10:27,399 --> 00:10:29,519
Here are some oral hygiene guidelines,

222
00:10:29,919 --> 00:10:30,919
along with my phone number.

223
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:32,279
If there's anything unclear,

224
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:33,320
or any discomfort,

225
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:35,080
feel free to contact me anytime.

226
00:10:37,879 --> 00:10:40,120
Thank you, Dr. Jiang.

227
00:10:41,399 --> 00:10:42,759
You're a good person.

228
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,960
A fine young man.

229
00:10:48,679 --> 00:10:50,080
We'll head back now.

230
00:10:50,559 --> 00:10:51,200
Let me see you out.

231
00:10:57,840 --> 00:10:58,600
Son,

232
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,559
you're a father now.

233
00:11:01,279 --> 00:11:02,759
You can't keep working yourself

234
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:05,360
day and night like before.

235
00:11:06,559 --> 00:11:08,519
Kids grow up in the blink of an eye.

236
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,919
If you don't spend time with him now,

237
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,759
later, even if you want to,

238
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:15,120
you won't get the chance.

239
00:11:32,799 --> 00:11:33,559
Lie down. Just lie back first.

240
00:11:33,639 --> 00:11:34,279
Doctor.

241
00:11:36,039 --> 00:11:37,000
My mouth here,

242
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:38,919
lately I don't know what's going on.

243
00:11:39,039 --> 00:11:39,759
It keeps bleeding.

244
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:42,000
And the mouth ulcers keep coming back.

245
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:44,559
I'm sure it's because of the tartar.

246
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:46,840
But my wife insists it's just Internal heat.

247
00:11:47,039 --> 00:11:47,960
She won't let me see a doctor.

248
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:48,960
And won't let me get my teeth cleaned.

249
00:11:49,120 --> 00:11:50,440
She says scaling makes teeth looser.

250
00:11:50,759 --> 00:11:52,720
If tartar isn't cleaned promptly,

251
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:53,799
it'll keep building up,

252
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:55,600
filling in the gaps between your teeth,

253
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:58,320
and then cause your gums to recede.

254
00:11:58,759 --> 00:12:00,279
And once we clean the tartar off,

255
00:12:00,399 --> 00:12:01,799
the gaps between teeth become visible.

256
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:03,320
At this point,

257
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:05,720
if someone has severe alveolar bone loss,

258
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:07,279
they'll feel their teeth becoming loose.

259
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:08,679
So that's why

260
00:12:08,759 --> 00:12:10,440
regular scaling is absolutely necessary.

261
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:12,360
Only by thoroughly removing the tartar

262
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:13,559
can we effectively prevent

263
00:12:13,759 --> 00:12:15,759
gum recession and periodontal disease.

264
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:17,559
Let me do a thorough exam first.

265
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:18,759
Okay.

266
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:30,159
You eat a lot of spicy food, don't you?

267
00:12:30,399 --> 00:12:30,879
It's pretty swollen.

268
00:12:30,919 --> 00:12:33,120
No, I usually eat pretty mild food.

269
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,360
This couldn't be...

270
00:12:42,879 --> 00:12:44,679
Here's what we'll do.

271
00:12:44,879 --> 00:12:46,159
I'll write you a slip first.

272
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:48,120
Please go to the lab for a blood test.

273
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:50,360
Then once the results are in, we'll...

274
00:12:50,519 --> 00:12:51,279
Hold on a second.

275
00:12:51,879 --> 00:12:52,960
I'm just here for a cleaning.

276
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:54,279
No need to make such a big deal, right?

277
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:56,480
Don't worry.

278
00:12:56,639 --> 00:12:58,720
It's just a routine check before scaling.

279
00:12:59,039 --> 00:12:59,960
